				<p class="uppercase mt-4 font-semibold">
					I've successfully launched web and desktop apps, optimized performance, and
					delivered seamless user experiences through my front-end
					development work. I'm excited to <span class="highlight"> continue growing</span> and
					contributing my skills to innovative projects.
